title: Stepping Heavenward
creator: E. Prentiss
description: Stepping Heavenward is the journal of a girl named Katherine Mortimer. Katy meets a young man who she loves & wants to marry but her mother is very much against their plans. But Katy’s life goes on through her marriage & motherhood and many tragedies. Her life is a constant struggle to step heavenward. reviews.reviewbody: This is a journal of prayer life and spiritual development of a young girl through womanhood.  It is mostly theology. The first and very last part of the book are interesting but it loses any plot in the middle.
